cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a few-shot learning method for classification and detection tasks using image-level class labels. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The method involves end-to-end training of a non-parametric star-model classifier, which suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of heatmaps for localization, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
